Furthermore, the rising awareness among healthcare providers and patients about the benefits of oxytocin injections in obstetric care is also contributing to market expansion. Oxytocin injections play a vital role in labor induction and are administered in cases where there is a need to expedite the childbirth process safely. As a result, healthcare facilities such as hospitals, clinics, and maternity centers are increasing their adoption of oxytocin injections to ensure better maternal outcomes. This trend is expected to continue driving market growth in the coming years as more healthcare providers recognize the importance of oxytocin in maternal health management.

